      <title>埃利奥特据称已持有巴菲特青睐的住友商事“大量”股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/elliott-said-to-build-large-stake-in-buffett-favored-sumitomo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，埃利奥特管理公司(Elliott Management Corp.)已持有住友商事株式会社(Sumitomo Corp.)的“大量”股份，住友商事株式会社是沃伦·巴菲特最喜欢的日本贸易公司之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/elliott-said-to-build-large-stake-in-buffett-favored-sumitomo</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 09:49:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在取消印度一周后，马斯克出人意料地访问中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/musk-makes-unannounced-china-visit-in-push-for-self-driving-cars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司首席执行官埃隆·马斯克(Elon Musk)周日对中国进行了一次未经宣布的访问，并会见了中国国务院总理李强。一周前，他推迟了对印度的访问，以处理该汽车制造商的紧迫问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/musk-makes-unannounced-china-visit-in-push-for-self-driving-cars</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 07:41:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
