      <title>东南亚热浪导致学校停课，引发电力需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/philippines-shuts-schools-as-heat-in-capital-busts-1915-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾宣布将停止公立学校的面授课程，而泰国的电力需求则升至创纪录水平，因为席卷南亚的热浪继续造成损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/philippines-shuts-schools-as-heat-in-capital-busts-1915-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 07:17:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
