      <title>泰国任命资本市场资深人士担任财务主管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/thailand-picks-capital-markets-veteran-pichai-as-finance-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理斯雷塔·塔维辛 (Srettha Thavisin) 任命资本市场资深人士皮查伊·春哈瓦吉拉 (Pichai Chunhavajira) 为泰国新任财政部长，这一任命可能会缓解总理与央行之间在货币政策方面的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/thailand-picks-capital-markets-veteran-pichai-as-finance-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 04:43:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
